data.description: This very well-cared for home has room for everyone. Four bedrooms and three bathrooms with an office or additional family room downstairs means there is plenty of room. The decks are well maintained with outstanding views and privacy.  You'll feel miles away, but with all the conveniences of living close to town. One of the home's best features are the solar panels, giving the buyer of this home a $12.95 monthly electric bill all year long! Don't miss viewing this quiet, peaceful home!
